 -of default=noprint_wrappers=1:nokey=1 "$VIDEO_PATH")

ffmpeg -y -i "$VIDEO_PATH" -i "$TITLE_PATH" \

nodes.name: Overlay Hook Title
nodes.notes:
#!/bin/bash

VIDEO_PATH="/tmp/heygen_avatar.mp4"
TITLE_PATH="/tmp/overlay_image.png"
MUSIC_PATH="/tmp/backgroundmusic.flac"

echo "–û–±—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∫–∞ –° –º—É–∑—ã–∫–æ–π"

if [ ! -f "$VIDEO_PATH" ] || [ ! -f "$TITLE_PATH" ] || [ ! -f "$MUSIC_PATH" ]; then
   echo "–û–®–ò–ë–ö–ê: –§–∞–π–ª—ã –Ω–µ –Ω–∞–π–¥–µ–Ω—ã!"
   exit 1
fi

ffmpeg -y \
 -i "$VIDEO_PATH" \
 -i "$TITLE_PATH" \
 -i "$MUSIC_PATH" \
 -filter_complex "
   [1:v]scale=iw/3:ih/3[title_scaled];
   [0:v][title_scaled]overlay=(W-w)/2:100:enable='between(t,0,1)'[v];
   [2:a]volume=0.1,afade=in:st=0:d=1,afade=out:st=20:d=2[audio_bg];
   [0:a][audio_bg]amix=inputs=2:duration=shortest:weights=1 0.1[audio_mixed]
 " \
 -map "[v]" -map "[audio_mixed]" \
 -c:v libx264 -c:a aac \
 /tmp/video_final.mp4

echo "–ì–û–¢–û–í–û!"
